██╔════╝██╔═══██╗██╔══██╗██╔════╝    ██╔══██╗██║
██║     ██║   ██║██████╔╝█████╗      ███████║██║
██║     ██║   ██║██╔══██╗██╔══╝      ██╔══██║██║
╚██████╗╚██████╔╝██║  ██║███████╗    ██║  ██║██║
 ╚═════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝    ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝
</pre>
                            </div>
                            <div class="deep-research">
                                ============ DEEP RESEARCH PRIVACY ============
                            </div>
                            <div class="boot-sequence">
                                <p>[SYSTEM] Initializing CORE AI subsystems...</p>
                                <p>[SYSTEM] Loading research modules...</p>
                                <p>[SYSTEM] Connecting to Venice.ai...</p>
                                <p>[SYSTEM] Connecting to Brave Search...</p>
                                <p>[SYSTEM] All systems operational.</p>
                                <p>[SYSTEM] CORE AI terminal ready. Type <span class="cmd-highlight">help</span> for commands.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="terminal-input-line">
                            <span class="prompt">&gt;</span>
                            <input type="text" id="command-input" autocomplete="off" autofocus>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-bar">
                        <div class="progress-bar">
                            <div id="progress-fill"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="progress-text">Ready</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/terminal.js"></script>
</body>
</html>